INSERT INTO public.compliance_results (result_id, loan_id, checked_at, control_results, compliance_score, overall_status, breach_explanations, severity) VALUES ('05f27f68-0521-42e6-a7af-3eec387f4f82', 'LN-10033', '2026-02-25T21:39:40.412826', '{''control_1'': True, ''control_2'': True, ''control_3'': False, ''control_4'': True, ''control_5'': True, ''control_6'': True, ''control_7'': True, ''control_8'': False, ''control_9'': True, ''control_10'': True}', 8, 'BREACH', '**CONTROL_3 — Stress Test**  
The loan for Yuki Jackson failed the stress test requirement, as the borrower did not meet the minimum qualifying rate of the contract rate plus 2%. According to OSFI B-20 Section 2, all borrowers must pass this stress test to ensure they can manage their mortgage payments under potential interest rate increases. This breach poses a significant risk to the institution, as it may lead to higher default rates if borrowers are not adequately assessed for their ability to withstand financial strain, ultimately impacting the institution''s financial stability.

**CONTROL_8 — Closing Disclosure Timing**  
The closing disclosure for Yuki Jackson was not sent at least 3 business days prior to closing, which is a violation of federal mortgage disclosure rules. This requirement exists to ensure that borrowers have sufficient time to review the terms of their mortgage and make informed decisions before finalizing the loan. Failing to comply with this timing requirement increases the risk of borrower dissatisfaction and potential legal repercussions for the institution, as it undermines the transparency and trust essential in the lending process.', 'High') ON CONFLICT (result_id) DO NOTHING;
